1.title: Spreading My Wings

episode of.title: Bristol Palin: Life's a Tripp (TV Series 2012– )

1.plot: Bristol welcomes viewers into the Palin household as she prepares to say goodbye to her hometown, Wasilla, Alaska for a few months. But first, she has to convince her reluctant younger sister, Willow, to come with her and her son, Tripp, to Los Angeles.

2.title: From Bad to Worse

episode of.title: Bristol Palin: Life's a Tripp (TV Series 2012– )

2.plot: While enjoying a night out on the town with friends, Bristol encounters a very aggressive critic of the Palin family; her response makes headlines.

3.title: Bristol, a Book and the Beach

episode of.title: Bristol Palin: Life's a Tripp (TV Series 2012– )

3.plot: Levi Johnston's (Bristol's ex-boyfriend and father to her son Tripp) tell-all book is published while Bristol struggles to adjust to life in LA. Bristol begs Willow to return so that she doesn't have to face the media storm alone.

4.title: Baby Daddy Dilemma

episode of.title: Bristol Palin: Life's a Tripp (TV Series 2012– )

4.plot: Back in Alaska, Bristol arranges for a meeting between her, Levi and Tripp to discuss Levi's role in Tripp's life. Willow opposes the idea of giving Levi another chance, while Andy suggests Tripp is better off without a part-time Dad.

5.title: Ms. Palin Goes to Washington

episode of.title: Bristol Palin: Life's a Tripp (TV Series 2012– )

5.plot: Bristol and Willow join Sarah on her trip to Washington, DC for the CPAC convention. While in DC, Bristol encounters hecklers, hosts a book signing and comes face to face with a Sarah Palin impersonator/imposter.

6.title: Sarah's Surprise

episode of.title: Bristol Palin: Life's a Tripp (TV Series 2012– )

6.plot: Bristol, Willow and the family plan a surprise birthday party for Sarah. In the midst of the planning, Bristol realizes that Tripp's discipline issues have gotten out of hand and the entire family weighs in on what should be done.

7.title: Valen-Times

episode of.title: Bristol Palin: Life's a Tripp (TV Series 2012– )

7.plot: Valentine's Day is near and both love and hate are in the air. Gino surprises Bristol with a distinctively Alaskan gift while Willow proves there's no love lost between her and Bristol.

8.title: Reindeer Games

episode of.title: Bristol Palin: Life's a Tripp (TV Series 2012– )

8.plot: Bristol, Gino and Andy prepare Tripp for his first Iron Pup race. Along the way, Bristol does a radio interview, encounters her biggest fear and cheers Todd along at the start of his Iron Dog snow machine race.

9.title: Cabin Fever

episode of.title: Bristol Palin: Life's a Tripp (TV Series 2012– )

9.plot: Willow takes a tour of Trendsetters Beauty School in Anchorage and contemplates her future while Bristol, Gino and Tripp spend their first vacation together en route to the Iron Dog finish line in Fairbanks, Alaska.

10.title: New Beginnings

episode of.title: Bristol Palin: Life's a Tripp (TV Series 2012– )

10.plot: Bristol and Willow visit Phoenix, AZ. Willow explores a local hair school while Bristol finalizes the sale of an investment property as she prepares to move into her new lake house in Wasilla.

11.title: Bearizona

episode of.title: Bristol Palin: Life's a Tripp (TV Series 2012– )

11.plot: Bristol, Tripp and Gino head southwest to check in on Willow at hair school in Arizona. Following a trip to the taxidermist in an attempt to make Willow's apartment more Alaskan, Bristol and Gino soak in local culture.

12.title: Kicked to the Curb

episode of.title: Bristol Palin: Life's a Tripp (TV Series 2012– )

12.plot: Before driving to Alaska with a moving truck packed with her belongings, Bristol and Co. take a quick road trip to the Grand Canyon.

13.title: The Bet

episode of.title: Bristol Palin: Life's a Tripp (TV Series 2012– )

13.plot: With Gino out of the picture, Bristol welcomes her struggling single-mom friend, Marissa, and her young daughter to move in with her in Wasilla. A trip to a maternity house provides an eye-opening experience for the young single moms and Willow.

14.title: The Ring Bear-Er

episode of.title: Bristol Palin: Life's a Tripp (TV Series 2012– )

14.plot: After making amends, Bristol and Gino take major steps in their relationship. But before Gino can put a ring on it, he needs to clear the air with disapproving sister Willow.

imdb.plot outline: This is about the life of Bristol Palin while on an amazing journey through life. As a single mother caught up in a love story. As she goes in out of relationships, it shows that her whole world is about the love of her life, Tripp who is her son.
